{"tid":1836574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[肺炎助攻 文宣埋門] 呢單野揭露左中共同港府有幾撚仆街同垃圾。","createTime":"2020-01-23T09:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T14:48:40.000Z","uid":51171,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f07515826dd722a7591f347e14254160c01e11","tid":1836574,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"點解香港人唔想痴埋中國到？<br />\n點解香港人要反呢個政府？<br />\n<br />\n<ins>中：</ins><br />\n- 一國一制下嘅醫療系統有幾垃圾<br />\n- 封鎖消息，冇新聞同言論自由<br />\n- 垃圾文化，狗屎垃圾都擺入口<br />\n- 垃圾管治，有SARS經驗仍然搞唔掂件事，仲愈來愈大獲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>港：</ins><br />\n- 垃圾管治，反應遲緩，防疫變抗疫<br />\n- 奶共重要過香港市民條命，唔收緊入境管制，到呢一刻仲中門大開，任由大陸人自出自入，仲要推港珠澳免費任行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 政治凌駕人命，死都唔戴口罩，仲繼續爭取緊「禁蒙面法」成法<br />\n- 橫蠻固執，唔聽專家意見。死堅持高鐵旅客唔洗申報，最終奶野。到呢刻仲唔肯對武漢發旅遊警示，對家都已經封埋城。總之所有意見都ban!ban!ban!左先。"},{"pid":"3638602d66beb1191141ea3f89047c8262f379b4","tid":1836574,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62fae2ee4294cd53856ae239278577744dd4e85e","tid":1836574,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0476481c7d51817563ec4716f573645e8cd864","tid":1836574,"uid":188393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"Cls國家"},{"pid":"68d00a69c61150fe96767a05703a662a199fa402","tid":1836574,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"4ef89cb91cb44725aad9de49bfa78464b98d450c","tid":1836574,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1459bb1cfe1ea68ea19d48dc64952c27fef035a4","tid":1836574,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"600aaf7bc7f3e130999a306d2d61dcfa240140ba"